{"data":[{"name":"87:1","price":"അത്യുന്നതനായ നിന്‍റെ രക്ഷിതാവിന്‍റെ നാമം നീ പ്രകീര്‍ത്തിക്കുക.","arabic":"سَبِّحِ ٱسۡمَ رَبِّكَ ٱلۡأَعۡلَى","category":["87 (Al-A'la)","Al-A'la","Surah Al-A'la"],"ayahNumber":5949,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ml","meta":{"transliteration":"sabbiḥi is'ma rabbika al-aʿlā ","translations":["Glorify","(the) name","(of) your Lord","the Most High","(1)"],"transliterationArr":["sabbiḥi","is'ma","rabbika","al-aʿlā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,880],[2,880,1280],[3,1280,2150],[4,2150,3995]]}},{"name":"87:2","price":"സൃഷ്ടിക്കുകയും, സംവിധാനിക്കുകയും ചെയ്ത (രക്ഷിതാവിന്‍റെ).","arabic":"ٱلَّذِي خَلَقَ فَسَوَّىٰ","category":["87 (Al-A'la)","Al-A'la","Surah Al-A'la"],"ayahNumber":5950,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ml","meta":{"transliteration":"alladhī khalaqa fasawwā ","translations":["The One Who","created","then proportioned","(2)"],"transliterationArr":["alladhī","khalaqa","fasawwā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1020],[2,1020,1680],[3,1680,2915]]}},{"name":"87:3","price":"വ്യവസ്ഥ നിര്‍ണയിച്ചു മാര്‍ഗദര്‍ശനം നല്‍കിയവനുമായവനെ.(1)","arabic":"وَٱلَّذِي قَدَّرَ فَهَدَىٰ","category":["87 (Al-A'la)","Al-A'la","Surah Al-A'la"],"ayahNumber":5951,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"1) പ്രകൃതിയിലെ സചേതനവും അചേതനവുമായ മുഴുവന്‍ വസ്തുക്കള്‍ക്കും കണിശവും സൂക്ഷ്മവുമായ വ്യവസ്ഥ അല്ലാഹു നല്കിയിട്ടുണ്ട്. ഓരോ വസ്തുവും എങ്ങനെ വര്‍ത്തിക്കണമെന്നത് സംബന്ധിച്ച മാര്‍ഗദര്‍ശനവും അതോടൊപ്പം അവന്‍ നല്കിയിട്ടുണ്ട്.","lang":"ml","meta":{"transliteration":"wa-alladhī qaddara fahadā ","translations":["And the One Who","measured","then guided","(3)"],"transliterationArr":["wa-alladhī","qaddara","fahadā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1000],[2,1000,1840],[3,1840,2915]]}},{"name":"87:4","price":"മേച്ചില്‍ പുറങ്ങള്‍ ഉല്‍പാദിപ്പിച്ചവനും,","arabic":"وَٱلَّذِيٓ أَخۡرَجَ ٱلۡمَرۡعَىٰ","category":["87 (Al-A'la)","Al-A'la","Surah Al-A'la"],"ayahNumber":5952,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ml","meta":{"transliteration":"wa-alladhī akhraja al-marʿā ","translations":["And the One Who","brings forth","the pasture","(4)"],"transliterationArr":["wa-alladhī","akhraja","al-marʿā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,2600],[2,2600,3310],[3,3310,4535]]}},{"name":"87:5","price":"എന്നിട്ട് അതിനെ ഉണങ്ങിക്കരിഞ്ഞ ചവറാക്കി തീര്‍ത്തവനുമായ (രക്ഷിതാവിന്‍റെ നാമം).","arabic":"فَجَعَلَهُۥ غُثَآءً أَحۡوَىٰ","category":["87 (Al-A'la)","Al-A'la","Surah Al-A'la"],"ayahNumber":5953,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ml","meta":{"transliteration":"fajaʿalahu ghuthāan aḥwā ","translations":["And then makes it","stubble","dark","(5)"],"transliterationArr":["fajaʿalahu","ghuthāan","aḥwā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1250],[2,1250,3780],[3,3780,4795]]}},{"name":"87:6","price":"നിനക്ക് നാം ഓതിത്തരാം. നീ മറന്നു പോകുകയില്ല.","arabic":"سَنُقۡرِئُكَ فَلَا تَنسَىٰٓ","category":["87 (Al-A'la)","Al-A'la","Surah Al-A'la"],"ayahNumber":5954,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ml","meta":{"transliteration":"sanuq'ri-uka falā tansā ","translations":["We will make you recite","so not","you will forget","(6)"],"transliterationArr":["sanuq'ri-uka","falā","tansā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1330],[2,1330,1980],[3,1980,3675]]}},{"name":"87:7","price":"അല്ലാഹു ഉദ്ദേശിച്ചതൊഴികെ.(2) തീര്‍ച്ചയായും അവന്‍ പരസ്യമായതും, രഹസ്യമായിരിക്കുന്നതും അറിയുന്നു.","arabic":"إِلَّا مَا شَآءَ ٱللَّهُۚ إِنَّهُۥ يَعۡلَمُ ٱلۡجَهۡرَ وَمَا يَخۡفَىٰ","category":["87 (Al-A'la)","Al-A'la","Surah Al-A'la"],"ayahNumber":5955,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"2) ഖുര്‍ആനില്‍ നിന്ന് ഏതെങ്കിലും ഭാഗം നബി(ﷺ) മറന്നുപോകുമെന്ന് ഇതിനര്‍ത്ഥമില്ല. ഓര്‍മശക്തി പോലെ തന്നെ മറവിയും അല്ലാഹുവിന്റെ ഒരു അനുഗ്രഹമാണ്. ചില കടുത്ത ദുരനുഭവങ്ങള്‍ മറക്കുവാന്‍ കഴിയേണ്ടത് ജീവിതയാഥാര്‍ഥ്യങ്ങളെ വിജയകരമായി അഭിമുഖീകരിക്കുന്നതിന് അനുപേക്ഷ്യമാണ്. നബി(ﷺ) എന്തൊക്കെ ഓര്‍മിക്കണമെന്നും എന്തൊക്കെ വിസ്മരിക്കണമെന്നും അല്ലാഹു തീരുമാനിക്കുന്നു.","lang":"ml","meta":{"transliteration":"illā mā shāa al-lahu innahu yaʿlamu al-jahra wamā yakhfā ","translations":["Except","what","wills","Allah","Indeed, He","knows","the manifest","and what","is hidden","(7)"],"transliterationArr":["illā","mā","shāa","al-lahu","innahu","yaʿlamu","al-jahra","wamā","yakhfā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,870],[2,870,1230],[3,1230,3290],[4,3290,6380],[5,6380,8130],[6,8130,9020],[7,9020,10030],[8,10030,10670],[9,10670,11645]]}},{"name":"87:8","price":"കൂടുതല്‍ എളുപ്പമുള്ളതിലേക്ക് നിനക്ക് നാം സൗകര്യമുണ്ടാക്കിത്തരുന്നതുമാണ്‌.","arabic":"وَنُيَسِّرُكَ لِلۡيُسۡرَىٰ","category":["87 (Al-A'la)","Al-A'la","Surah Al-A'la"],"ayahNumber":5956,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ml","meta":{"transliteration":"wanuyassiruka lil'yus'rā ","translations":["And We will ease you","to the ease","(8)"],"transliterationArr":["wanuyassiruka","lil'yus'rā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1510],[2,1510,3285]]}},{"name":"87:9","price":"അതിനാല്‍ ഉപദേശം ഫലപ്പെടുന്നുവെങ്കില്‍ നീ ഉപദേശിച്ചു കൊള്ളുക.","arabic":"فَذَكِّرۡ إِن نَّفَعَتِ ٱلذِّكۡرَىٰ","category":["87 (Al-A'la)","Al-A'la","Surah Al-A'la"],"ayahNumber":5957,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ml","meta":{"transliteration":"fadhakkir in nafaʿati al-dhik'rā ","translations":["So remind","if","benefits","the reminder","(9)"],"transliterationArr":["fadhakkir","in","nafaʿati","al-dhik'rā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,950],[2,950,1300],[3,1300,3070],[4,3070,4835]]}},{"name":"87:10","price":"ഭയപ്പെടുന്നവര്‍ ഉപദേശം സ്വീകരിച്ചു കൊള്ളുന്നതാണ്‌.","arabic":"سَيَذَّكَّرُ مَن يَخۡشَىٰ","category":["87 (Al-A'la)","Al-A'la","Surah Al-A'la"],"ayahNumber":5958,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ml","meta":{"transliteration":"sayadhakkaru man yakhshā ","translations":["He will pay heed ","(one) who","fears (Allah)","(10)"],"transliterationArr":["sayadhakkaru","man","yakhshā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1660],[2,1660,1900],[3,1900,4095]]}},{"name":"87:11","price":"ഏറ്റവും നിര്‍ഭാഗ്യവാനായിട്ടുള്ളവന്‍ അതിനെ (ഉപദേശത്തെ) വിട്ടകന്നു പോകുന്നതാണ്‌.","arabic":"وَيَتَجَنَّبُهَا ٱلۡأَشۡقَى","category":["87 (Al-A'la)","Al-A'la","Surah Al-A'la"],"ayahNumber":5959,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ml","meta":{"transliteration":"wayatajannabuhā al-ashqā ","translations":["And will avoid it","the wretched one","(11)"],"transliterationArr":["wayatajannabuhā","al-ashqā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,2420],[2,2420,4215]]}},{"name":"87:12","price":"വലിയ അഗ്നിയില്‍ കടന്ന് എരിയുന്നവനത്രെ അവന്‍.","arabic":"ٱلَّذِي يَصۡلَى ٱلنَّارَ ٱلۡكُبۡرَىٰ","category":["87 (Al-A'la)","Al-A'la","Surah Al-A'la"],"ayahNumber":5960,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ml","meta":{"transliteration":"alladhī yaṣlā al-nāra al-kub'rā ","translations":["The one who","will burn","(in) the Fire","[the] great","(12)"],"transliterationArr":["alladhī","yaṣlā","al-nāra","al-kub'rā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1120],[2,1120,1680],[3,1680,3400],[4,3400,5055]]}},{"name":"87:13","price":"പിന്നീട് അവന്‍ അതില്‍ മരിക്കുകയില്ല. ജീവിക്കുകയുമില്ല.(3)","arabic":"ثُمَّ لَا يَمُوتُ فِيهَا وَلَا يَحۡيَىٰ","category":["87 (Al-A'la)","Al-A'la","Surah Al-A'la"],"ayahNumber":5961,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"3) യാതൊരുവിധ സുഖവും സന്തോഷവുമില്ലാത്ത, ദുരിതപൂര്‍ണമായ നരകജീവിതം യഥാര്‍ഥത്തില്‍ ജീവിതമെന്ന് പറയാന്‍ അര്‍ഹമല്ല. മരണത്തിലൂടെ ആ ദുരിതത്തിന് അവസാനമുണ്ടായെങ്കില്‍ എന്ന് നരകാവകാശികള്‍ കൊതിക്കും. എന്നാല്‍ അല്ലാഹു അവര്‍ക്ക് മരണം വിധിക്കുകയില്ല.","lang":"ml","meta":{"transliteration":"thumma lā yamūtu fīhā walā yaḥyā ","translations":["Then","not","he will die","therein","and not","will live","(13)"],"transliterationArr":["thumma","lā","yamūtu","fīhā","walā","yaḥyā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1650],[2,1650,2180],[3,2180,3100],[4,3100,4010],[5,4010,4740],[6,4740,5865]]}},{"name":"87:14","price":"തീര്‍ച്ചയായും പരിശുദ്ധി നേടിയവൻ വിജയം പ്രാപിച്ചു.","arabic":"قَدۡ أَفۡلَحَ مَن تَزَكَّىٰ","category":["87 (Al-A'la)","Al-A'la","Surah Al-A'la"],"ayahNumber":5962,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ml","meta":{"transliteration":"qad aflaḥa man tazakkā ","translations":["Certainly","has succeeded","(one) who","purifies (himself)","(14)"],"transliterationArr":["qad","aflaḥa","man","tazakkā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,350],[2,350,1250],[3,1250,2400],[4,2400,3865]]}},{"name":"87:15","price":"തന്‍റെ രക്ഷിതാവിന്‍റെ നാമം സ്മരിക്കുകയും എന്നിട്ട് നമസ്കരിക്കുകയും (ചെയ്തവന്‍).","arabic":"وَذَكَرَ ٱسۡمَ رَبِّهِۦ فَصَلَّىٰ","category":["87 (Al-A'la)","Al-A'la","Surah Al-A'la"],"ayahNumber":5963,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ml","meta":{"transliteration":"wadhakara is'ma rabbihi faṣallā ","translations":["And remembers","(the) name","(of) his Lord","and prays","(15)"],"transliterationArr":["wadhakara","is'ma","rabbihi","faṣallā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,790],[2,790,1290],[3,1290,2390],[4,2390,3635]]}},{"name":"87:16","price":"പക്ഷെ, നിങ്ങള്‍ ഐഹിക ജീവിതത്തിന്ന് കൂടുതല്‍ പ്രാധാന്യം നല്‍കുന്നു.","arabic":"بَلۡ تُؤۡثِرُونَ ٱلۡحَيَوٰةَ ٱلدُّنۡيَا","category":["87 (Al-A'la)","Al-A'la","Surah Al-A'la"],"ayahNumber":5964,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ml","meta":{"transliteration":"bal tu'thirūna al-ḥayata al-dun'yā ","translations":["Nay","You prefer","the life","(of) the world","(16)"],"transliterationArr":["bal","tu'thirūna","al-ḥayata","al-dun'yā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,410],[2,410,1620],[3,1620,2760],[4,2760,4015]]}},{"name":"87:17","price":"പരലോകമാകുന്നു ഏറ്റവും ഉത്തമവും നിലനില്‍ക്കുന്നതും.","arabic":"وَٱلۡأٓخِرَةُ خَيۡرٞ وَأَبۡقَىٰٓ","category":["87 (Al-A'la)","Al-A'la","Surah Al-A'la"],"ayahNumber":5965,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ml","meta":{"transliteration":"wal-ākhiratu khayrun wa-abqā ","translations":["While the Hereafter","(is) better","and everlasting","(17)"],"transliterationArr":["wal-ākhiratu","khayrun","wa-abqā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1580],[2,1580,3190],[3,3190,4805]]}},{"name":"87:18","price":"തീര്‍ച്ചയായും ഇത് ആദ്യത്തെ ഏടുകളില്‍ തന്നെയുണ്ട്‌.","arabic":"إِنَّ هَٰذَا لَفِي ٱلصُّحُفِ ٱلۡأُولَىٰ","category":["87 (Al-A'la)","Al-A'la","Surah Al-A'la"],"ayahNumber":5966,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ml","meta":{"transliteration":"inna hādhā lafī al-ṣuḥufi al-ūlā ","translations":["Indeed","this","surely (is) in","the Scriptures","[the] former","(18)"],"transliterationArr":["inna","hādhā","lafī","al-ṣuḥufi","al-ūlā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1460],[2,1460,2360],[3,2360,2740],[4,2740,3700],[5,3700,4865]]}},{"name":"87:19","price":"അതായത് ഇബ്റാഹീമിന്‍റെയും മൂസായുടെയും ഏടുകളില്‍.(4)","arabic":"صُحُفِ إِبۡرَٰهِيمَ وَمُوسَىٰ","category":["87 (Al-A'la)","Al-A'la","Surah Al-A'la"],"ayahNumber":5967,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"4) പാപപുണ്യങ്ങളെയും മോക്ഷത്തെയും പറ്റി വിശുദ്ധഖുര്‍ആനില്‍ പ്രതിപാദിച്ച കാര്യങ്ങളുടെ സാരാംശം പൂര്‍വപ്രവാചകന്മാര്‍ക്ക് നല്കപ്പെട്ട വേദങ്ങളിലുള്ളത് തന്നെയാണ് എന്നര്‍ത്ഥം.","lang":"ml","meta":{"transliteration":"ṣuḥufi ib'rāhīma wamūsā ","translations":["(The) Scriptures","(of) Ibrahim","and Musa","(19)"],"transliterationArr":["ṣuḥufi","ib'rāhīma","wamūsā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,830],[2,830,2360],[3,2360,4025]]}}],"chapter":["87 (Al-A'la)","Al-A'la","Surah Al-A'la","Chapter Al-A'la","A'la","Surah A'la","Chapter A'la","Al A'la","Surah Al A'la","Chapter Al A'la","Surah 87","Chapter 87","The Most High","الأعلى"],"version":{"key":"malayalam_kunhi","direction":"ltr","language_iso_code":"ml","version":"1.0.3","last_update":1622322000,"title":"Malayalam translation - Abdul-Hamid Haidar Al-Madany and Kanhi Muhammad","description":"Translation of the Quran meanings into Malayalam by Abdul-Hamid Haidar Al-Madany and Kanhi Muhammad."}}